title: Toontrack Superior Drummer v2.4.1 Incl. Keygen-R2R [ATOM]

Description:
Superior Drummer is the award-winning, professional drum production studio aimed at the user looking for total control in any aspect imaginable when it comes to producing drums.

With its unrivaled sample engine, phenomenal sound shaping tools and extensive feature list, Superior Drummer 2.0 truly sets the benchmark in modern drum production.Superior Drummer 2.0 comes with 20 GB of meticulously sampled quality drums, recorded in the legendary Avatar Studios in New York City by engineer duo Neil Dorfsman and Pat Thrall together with drummer Nir Z.
